column2: SELECT Top # g.ra, g.dec, g.AGCNr, n.objid, n.distance, o.ra AS ra_SDSS, o.dec AS dec_SDSS, o.objID, o.u, o.g, o.r, o.i, o.z, o.err_u, o.err_g, o.err_r, o.err_i, o.err_z, o.expRad_r, o.expRadErr_r, o.deVRad_r, o.deVRadErr_r, o.petroRad_r, o.petroRadErr_r, o.mode -- INTO MyDB.CGM_ALF_SDSS FROM MyDB.CGM_ALF_TST AS g CROSS APPLY DR1#.dbo.fGetNearbyObjAllEq (g.ra, g.dec, #) AS n JOIN DR1#.PhotoPrimary AS o ON n.objid = o.objid
